{"tid":1745020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 若當日有票站未能完成投票，會安排在後備投票日再投票","createTime":"2019-11-22T04:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:49:25.000Z","uid":50972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87cf37429aa76978e6fb1bd8850e4d104196299e","tid":1745020,"uid":50972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"聶德權解釋，若當日有票站未能完成投票，會安排在後備投票日再投票。例如當日在下午兩點暫停投票，會安排在後備投票日兩點再投票，讓整個投票都是在早上七時半至晚上10時半期間進行。聶德權又說，注意到網上有人說在早上完成投票後，下午就破壞票站。他說，整個投票是在早上7時半到晚上10時半完成，才可以開始點票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如當日個別票站因情況混亂而需中止投票，會安排在後備投票日（12月1日）的同一時間，繼續進行餘下投票程序。"},{"pid":"dae2bc2fcebec7ddaa35d3b168c55c66190c5137","tid":1745020,"uid":50972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af6fabcda3cc7921d1387c6ee0d234ca19ff207","tid":1745020,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b390cf7a85a692042f572e97d616914bce1f403","tid":1745020,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"中間票箱任佢舞"},{"pid":"75f93c90043614ccdb443d5ed33402b07ddf1370","tid":1745020,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"方便換票箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010ed64fdf38ac7fc8f2073afbe558715f9f83c9","tid":1745020,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:36:25.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"4b3c04c9c21553b976aa18acce01606ce5901212","tid":1745020,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b390cf7a85a692042f572e97d616914bce1f403","tid":1745020,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"中間票箱任佢舞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f1ca15984b5138472059a200e888dbeddd50eb","tid":1745020,"uid":50972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"大家想早去投定遲去投自己話事<br />\n只係想大家正視返一d正確既資訊<br />\n唔好攪到自己成個廢老咁"}]}